{
  "stem": "15174.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We lived-- we stayed in New York for a month.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm glad you reminded me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- you know, we had to-- we had to pass through customs, but the kids were running around, and we were running around in the-- there was sort of a hangar-like area in the pier where all our luggage was.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And where actually, we ran outside, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a large crowd of people apparently awaiting the passengers on the ship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had seen pictures of my great uncle and my grandfather who were in New York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought that they might be there, and I looked and I thought I recognized them, but I didn't have the guts to go up and say I'm Sol Messinger.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Are you so and so?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It turned out that they were-- that was my grandfather and my great uncle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other thing that I remember was we had gone through customs and-- and a friend of mine and I were-- this friend had lived in [INAUDIBLE], in the-- the town near our village, and they were on the ship too.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- we-- you know, we were good friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after we had cleared customs, we had-- we each had French comic books.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we decided we would exchange comic books.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- one of the guards saw this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he-- he took us and he-- he asked us what we were doing, or somebody must have spoken in French or German because I understood.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- or he asked our parents what-- what-- what-- he thought we were maybe exchanging information.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my-- I remember my mother, she could have killed me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
